        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>State Harassment and Assault Prevention and Eradication Act of 2020 or the SHAPE Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill establishes policies, employee rights, and accountability measures to address harassment, discrimination, sexual assault, and related retaliation in the Department of State. </p>]]></text>
